Comment: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:26.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying and go to sleep already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:51.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Asleep already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:03.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Back at last?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:14.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you didn't go out to dispose of him, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:16.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I went to dispose of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you couldn't bring yourself? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:18.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:22.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at the very least,\Nyou'll make Lucy-May delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:29.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, what's the matter with you?\NDoing that at so late an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I like to sleep at night just like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:37.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But tonight, as soon as I'm asleep, I'm roused,\Nas soon as I fall asleep - roused again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:39.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So now I cannot even shut my eyes. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, it was actually all your fault. \NBecause you took that din...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What now, fell asleep already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well aintcha a lucky fella? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, and I don't want to sleep at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:06.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Going to pee?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:08.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:47.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad! So he didn't get rid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:00.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it too early yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:01.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm awake! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:04.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right. You woke up in the middle of the night, too... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:06.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:11.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I hope Ben returned while we were asleep. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:12.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He did return.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:14.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How would you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:15.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:17.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So you did wake up in the middle of the night!
Comment: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:19.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:34.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! The puppy is sleeping right here! 
Comment: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:35.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:38.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think Doctor is about to fall, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wake him up. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:42.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you'll fall from the bed this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:45.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't have the breakfast yet. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:49.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get any rest last night.\NYou just leave me to sleep like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:53.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie! Whenever I came here,\Nyou were fast asleep, snoring loudly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure, sure, sure... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:57.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Good morning, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:04.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I spent the whole evening crying,\Nthinking you'd done away with the puppy! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:05.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I actually went to do away with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought doing away with it\Nis the best thing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:13.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I just couldn't. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:16.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I ain't letting anyone\Ndo away with it from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:21.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But dad and mom said,\Nthe sooner we do away with it - the better, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:22.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask them to rethink! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:24.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:29.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you actually intend to take seriously\Nthe bringing up of this baby dingo? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:30.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,'Course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And you do realize it may be dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:34.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:36.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:38.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll also have to take action\Nif it starts troubling others. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:39.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:42.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that I can become best friends\Nwith this wild dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:47.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And if we become true friends,\Nthis dog won't have any reason to turn against me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You're awake, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little one! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:58.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:01.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This fella has one side that I'm finding a little odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:05.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which is him being a scaredy-cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:05.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Scaredy-cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Must be mighty hungry, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:19.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get some milk for you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:21.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here just one moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:28.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So he never abandoned the puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:31.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:39.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara, can I have some of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:43.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you tell mom already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Was planning to, after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:48.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:49.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:59.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God. I guess you can consider Sticky\Nyour wet nurse now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:04.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go introduce him to Marsh now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:14.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's still thirsty.\NCan you pour a bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It really doesn't look one bit dangerous! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to be an awful scaredy-cat, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:20.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:30.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, he's an awful poltroon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:11.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If he remains this way even when he's big,\Nhe won't cause us any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:13.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm still not entirely happy with it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Better that than becoming feral. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:21.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even a normal dog would've been\Na bit more daring than that. 
Comment: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:34.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:54.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, Lucy-May. Come inside,\Nwe need to have a talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:58.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Hurry up inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:00.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen closely, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:03.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll allow you to keep that baby dingo\Nunder a set of conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me to adhere to these at all times. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:06.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,First condition:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:10.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,should that dog attack a person\Nor hurt someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:12.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,we'll put it down then and there. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:12.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:13.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you understand, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:20.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:23.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Secondly, be it the sheep or the poultry,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:26.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,in other words, if he attacks or hurts\Nany kind of livestock,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:31.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,we'll also have to kill him, or else set him free in the wilderness, away from any livestock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:32.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:33.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The third condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:37.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If that dog ends up\Nonly listening to Lucy-May's orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:41.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,ignoring whatever others tell him,\Nwe'll have to banish him to the woods. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:42.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:44.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No "buts".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:45.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:52.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you put your every effort into petting him,\Nany ferocious beast would become attached to you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:57.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But even then, it still remains the very same\Nferocious beast towards everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:05.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It is essential that the dog becomes friendly\Ntowards other people as well, not just you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And if it can't get friendly,\Nat least that it's not hostile. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:11.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of upbringing I want you to give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:15.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Think you could do it, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:18.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:20.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:24.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, is that fine by you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:26.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:28.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Though I still think it's best\Nthat we don't try to raise it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:30.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't forget that I opposed it\Nfrom the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:35.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:39.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then. It seems, I'm starving, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How about we hurry up to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We need to give him a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:51.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about "Little", Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:52.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:56.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This way, even when he grows big,\Nwe'll still call him by this name,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:59.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,filled with hopes of him remaining forever\Ncute and innocent, the way he is now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:01.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:03.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:04.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:06.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That settles him as Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:08.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:18.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll grow up to be a good boy, our Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:25.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:31.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My mind was so set on the dog matter,\NI kept forgetting to tell you something up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:32.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:35.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Firing of bricks didn't go as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:36.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:40.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:44.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For now, we'll have to build a new house\Nfor you and Dr. Deighton from simple dried bricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:49.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I was already starting wonder, "wouldn't it be nice\Nto live in a house from fired bricks?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:52.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Sorry to disappoint,\Nbut for now, that's not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:57.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow, I'll try to get help with making dried bricks from anyone who's not too preoccupied. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:22:01.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You say "starting tomorrow",\Nbut you've not done any preparations yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:03.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we'll divide the labor\Nbetween us two from now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:06.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it upon myself\Nto prepare a wooden form. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:09.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, you go buy some straw\Nand start chopping it up. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:10.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need to mix it with the clay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:18.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear? Starting tomorrow,\Nwe'll be helping making bricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.12,0:22:20.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And with no time to play around?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:21.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems so to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:25.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, this dog doesn't bite now, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:26.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:28.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.46,0:22:30.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Very well if so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:31.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm still sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:38.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He actually ran away,\Nafraid that Doctor might bite him, instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:40.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's surprisingly yellow of that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:42.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:45.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If our playtime ends tomorrow,\Nwhy don't we play to our heart's content today?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:46.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:49.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take Little along and go to the hill!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:52.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry, while we've no errands to run yet! 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.21,0:22:54.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's hurry! Little, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:55.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, after us, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:11.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:12.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:24.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:33.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy became completely obsessed\Nwith the baby dingo we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.98,0:23:42.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Little, when you become a full-grown dog,\Nyou won't turn against Lucy, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.67,0:23:45.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because Lucy is your friend, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.61,0:24:06.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because we stained our clothes\Nwhile making the bricks,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.24,0:24:08.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,we went to the river to do the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.23,0:24:11.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To make them as clean as possible,\Nwe've decided to wash ourselves altogether. 
